model.name: Mitrophanov2015 - Simulating extended Hockin Blood Coagulation Model under varied pH

body.p: Mathematical model of the blood coagulation cascade with new kinetic rates to simulate acidosis. Extended Hockin2002 model. Reused Mitrophanov2011 model with new parameters k: 5, 6, 7, 10, 15, 16, 17, 22, 26, 31, 32, 43 and 44.
